												<p class="history-para">In 1976, eight entrepreneurs left their secure corporate jobs because they believed a microprocessor had the potential to change the world. In the same decade, along with Apple, they shipped in-house designed 8-bit microcomputers. </p>
											</div>								
										</a>	
																						
							</div>							
